fulltitle: DAN MORGENSTERN REMEMBERS ARTIE SHAW, PART TWO, and COOTIE WILLIAMS (June 8, 2018)
title: DAN MORGENSTERN REMEMBERS ARTIE SHAW, PART TWO, and COOTIE WILLIAMS (June 8, 2018)
description: Remembering Artie as a "champion talker," and earlier -- at Bop City, his jealousy of Benny Goodman (with a comment about Leonard Feather) -- and a terrible review from Mike Levin; Artie's involvement with the House Un-American Affairs Committee, where he "named names."  Dan's late friendship with Artie, including mentions of Daryl Sherman, Loren Schoemberg, Lester Young, Louis, and Benny Carter.  And Cootie Williams' comments on Benny Goodmanand his early adulation of Louis.
